UNksz Mentor usho lokhu izolo ngesikhathi ethula ubufakazi kwikhomishini yeJaji uZondo ephenya ngokulawulwa koMbuso yidlanzana. Uthe wasuswa emzini wakwaGupta wayiswa eSahara Computers, inkampani yalo mndeni, emuva kokufika esikhumulweni sezindiza iOR Tambo International ngo-2010 ephuma eChina. Uthe wathintwa nguNksz Lakela Kaunda emtshela ukuthi uzoba nomhlangano nabantu bakwaGupta. UNksz Kaunda wayesebenzela owayengumengameli wezwe, uMnuz Jacob Zuma. “Ngesikhathi ngifika emzini wakwaGupta ngaphathwa kahle ngoba ngangilandwe yibona e-OR Tambo. Ngabuzwa wumpheki ukuthi ngingathanda ukudlani. Ngathi ngithanda i-mutton curry ne-chai tea.” Uthe ababemele lo mndeni bamthembisa isikhundla sokuba wuNgqongqoshe wamaBhizinisi kahumeni kodwa yena wayefuna ukubonana noMengameli Jacob Zuma kwazise izimemezelo ezinjalo zazenziwa nguye.